{{spoiler}} {{Infobox Character |name = Mysterious Enemy |image = XC3 Mysterious Giant 1.jpg |aliases = [[Moebius (boss)]], [[Moebius D & J]] |species = [[Moebius]] |age = |gender = |haircolor = |eyecolor = |appearances = {{XC3}} |voiceactorjp = }} The '''Mysterious Enemy''' (Japanese: {{lang|ja|謎の巨人}}, ''Nazo no Kyojin'', Mysterious Giant) is an enemy in {{XC3}}. He is the first [[Moebius]] encountered by the party.<ref>[https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/az3ha/ Official Japanese website]</ref>
== Story== While the six protagonists are at odds with each other on the battlefield, the Mysterious Enemy suddenly attacks them from afar, piercing [[Guernica Vandham]] through the chest with a projectile. The Mysterious Enemy then reveals himself, with [[Mwamba]] and [[Hackt]] in his hands, taunting the party to keep killing each other for its own benefit, promptly killing his two captives afterwards, enraging the parties of both nations, who now are working together to defeat this new foe. After beating his first phase, Guernica pilots one of the [[City]] machines to attempt to fight the Mysterious Enemy, but the machine is quickly destroyed without ever dealing any damage to the foe. With his life draining out from him, Guernica gambles everything on activating the [[Ouroboros Stone]] in order to turn the protagonists into [[Ouroboros]], which is successful, resulting in [[Noah]] and [[Mio]] Interlinking. The Mysterious Enemy reveals himself to be a [[Moebius]], and fights the party in his second phase. The new Ouroboros form is enough to fend off the Moebius, who then retreats from battle, but not before giving out a signal that declares the party as the "enemy of the world". Guernica then tells Noah and Mio with his dying breaths that this ''"real enemy"'' with overwhelming power does not belong either to [[Keves]] or [[Agnus]]. He thus advises them to reach [[Swordmarch]]. The Moebius can later be seen in the [[Amphitheater]], being chastised by other [[Consuls]] for fleeing from battle. {{clr}}
== Battle == {{Infobox Enemy |name = Mysterious Enemy |image = Mysterious_Enemy.jpg |caption = Mysterious Enemy |category = Boss |type = [[Moebius]] |level = 10 |area = [[Alfeto Valley]] ([[Gura Flava Lowlands]]) |spawntime = Story |respawn = No |movement = Ground |detection = |exp = 448 |cp = 55 |sp = 0 |gold = 0 |hp = 26,550 |strength = 83 |healing = 82 |dexterity = 47 |agility = 30 |physdef = 0% |ethdef = 15% |critrate = 0% |guardrate = 0% }} The '''Mysterious Enemy''' is a [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] in {{XC3}}. He is fought at level 10 in the [[Gura Flava Lowlands]] in [[Alfeto Valley]]. He is later fought named as [[Moebius (boss)|Moebius]], then it is fought and revealed as [[Moebius D & J]]. It is the first Moebius fought by the party. {{clr}}
